<h1>Sample Tag</h1>

<p>
  This page demonstrates a kinda pseudo custom tag in SSP
  using an explicit PageContext parameter and a function which can be invoked
  by the someLayoutUsingTemplateContext() to process the body (writing the output as a side effect).
</p>

<% import org.fusesource.scalate.sample.MyTags._ %>

<% someLayoutUsingTemplateContext(context) { %>
this is the body!
<% } %>
